# TapLaunch public distribution repository
# Whitelist: only documentation and release-policy files may be committed.

# Ignore everything by default
*

# Allow only public distribution files
!.gitignore
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!PRIVACY.md
!SUPPORT.md
!SECURITY.md
!EULA.md
!LICENSE.md

# Defense-in-depth blocklist (documentation of intent; redundant under whitelist)
.DS_Store
*.xcworkspace
*.xcodeproj
DerivedData/
build/
dist/
*.app
*.dmg
*.pkg
*.zip
.env
.env.*
*.p12
*.cer
*.mobileprovision
*.provisionprofile
AuthKey_*.p8
